---
import '../styles/global.css'
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SEO to AIO — Make the Shift | Rank4AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Google traffic is collapsing. Make the shift from SEO to AI Search Visibility. Free audit from Rank4AI.">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png">
</head>
<body class="bg-white min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-[600px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Rank4AI" class="h-8 mx-auto mb-12 opacity-60">

    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4">The Shift</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-teal leading-tight mb-6">SEO is Not Enough. AI Search is Here.</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">Google organic clicks down 17%. Paid clicks down 68%. That traffic moved to AI search.</p>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Ranking on Google does not mean you appear in AI answers. Different system. Different signals. Different work. We help UK businesses make the shift.</p>

    <div class="bg-off-white rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 text-left">
      <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-4 text-center">Get Your Free AI Search Visibility Audit</h2>
      <form class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your name" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email address" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <input type="url" placeholder="Website URL" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-border rounded-lg text-sm" required>
        <button type="submit" class="cta-primary w-full justify-center">Get My Free Audit &rarr;</button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted text-center mt-4">No commitment. We test all 6 AI platforms.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">Rank4AI Ltd · Company 16584507 · <a href="/" class="underline">rank4ai.co.uk</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
